06, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"a true testament\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"that human right\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"clean competition\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about experiencing the joy that sports bring to all of us,\\\" she said as she endorsed the staging of the first-ever Special Olympics Caribbean Beach Games.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.545663092848282e-20, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1672, \"end\": 1687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disney's_Caribbean_Beach_Resort\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caribbean Beach\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disney's_Caribbean_Beach_Resort\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disney's_Caribbean_Beach_Resort\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the joy\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the staging\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cudjoe-Lewis, who emphasised the importance of \\\"inclusive sporting environments for all\\\" and the need to \\\"teach children discipline\\\", said the three-day event - to be hosted at venues in both islands of Trinidad and Tobago - can help with character building.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\", \"score\": 0.9999997568918684, \"rank\": 2.431078592506266e-07, \"text\